            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) into matchsticks and discard the core[s]</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, keeping the <strong>whites</strong> and <strong>greens</strong> separate</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>peri peri sauce</strong> with your<strong> mayo </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>perinaise</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
