        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>apple matchsticks</strong>,<strong> sliced spring onion whites </strong>and 1/2 tbsp per person of the <strong>perinaise </strong>(save the rest for later!) in a separate bowl – this is your <strong>apple slaw</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
