        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> peri peri meat-free chick'n</strong> with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>apple slaw</strong> and the <strong>remaining perinaise</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion greens </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
